### 1. Get All Suppliers
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Suppliers

### 2. Get All Categories
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Categories

### 3. Get Products with Supplier and Category
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Products?$expand=supplier,category

### 4. Get Customers
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Customers

### 5. Get Sales Orders with Items
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/SalesOrders?$expand=items

### 6. Filter Products by Price
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Products?$filter=price gt 100

### 7. Sort Products by Price Descending
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/Products?$orderby=price desc

### 8. Product Catalog Report
GET http://localhost:4004/report/ProductCatalog

### 9. Order Report
GET http://localhost:4004/report/OrderReport

### 10. Low Stock Alert Report
GET http://localhost:4004/report/LowStockAlert

### 11. Purchase Orders with Items
GET http://localhost:4004/admin/PurchaseOrders?$expand=items

### 12. Deep Insert Sales Order
POST http://localhost:4004/admin/SalesOrders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "SO1001",
  "orderDate": "2026-06-03",
  "totalAmount": 5000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "status": "NEW",
  "items": [
    {
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 1000,
      "netAmount": 2000
    },
    {
      "quantity": 3,
      "unitPrice": 1000,
      "netAmount": 3000
    }
  ]
}